INSERT INTO `reviewsentence_1300` VALUES (1,14,52,'Then they say they are not compatible with the phone.'),(2,0,220,'I searched for over a year for a new Nokia phone and narrowed it down to two and this one won out.'),(3,3,7,'the only thing that i dont like is that even that i\'ve had for a long time, i still cant get used to the qwerty keyboard when you turn the phone, sometimes it really is a pain in the butt.'),(4,0,216,'This phone is great i have nothing bad to say about this phone but the customer service lacks in every category that makes this phone a 1 star.'),(5,2,26,'I gave this 3/5 stars because texting does need to get some getting use to.'),(6,3,321,'I had a lager amount invested in songs and apps so when I got the 920 I was happy to find out that when I plugged.'),(7,2,387,'Although the 920, 1020 and 1520 seem to be excellent devices, what made me go with an 820 is that while it may not be the best at any particular feature, it has all the features that I\'m looking for.'),(8,23,275,'The web browser stinks but Opera Mini takes care of that.5.'),(9,2,22,'Then the battery is almost dead after a couple of hours of non-use off the charger.'),(10,1,247,'The construction is just beautiful, the look and feel of the hardware is superb, cant say much about battery life since i didn\'t use it extensively, but i have used the E71 in the past and i reckon it should be pretty good (compared to my Evo 4G!!).'),(11,2,42,'The internet browser is surprisingly fast but the memory fills up very fast too, due to the small RAM.'),(12,5,147,'The recent Symbian Anna update has made the OS a bit more user friendly, although it\'s still far from iOS.Overall, this is a very good smartphone.'),(13,1,432,'the phone is partial unlocked, I can put my Digicel sim in the phone and it work for most features.'),(14,2,440,'I bought the Lumia 810 when it first came out and two years later, there\'s still no better option in specs that fits my minimum requirements.'),(15,13,136,'I have had it for a month now without any major problems.'),(16,3,103,'The solution online short of returning the phone was to put it in the freezer for a while....Now who spends big bucks on a cell phone to keep it in the freezer?'),(17,5,40,'And, if my cheek brushed the screen on other voicemail systems, it would activate a number on the screen causing the message to be deleted, passed, saved, etc.So I paid retail to my provider (GCI) for my next phone, an Alcatel qwerty candybar style phone.'),(18,11,115,'More savings.......and same great ipad experience!!!'),(19,0,252,'To make the long story short; I bought this device over a year ago.'),(20,44,117,'The tremendous improvement in battery life in power-saving mode essentially eliminates this problem.I would also mention that there is a battery monitor application available from the Nokia store that is quite useful, and I recommend it to anyone using an N8.'),(21,2,330,'Multi-task is also very smart.. it doesn\'t matter how many apps you have opened - I never noticed any loss in performance!- Wireless charging was a big surprise.'),(22,6,88,'I haven\'t even figured out 25% of this phone yet but I already like it.'),(23,21,118,'Ovi Maps (v3.06 which does not come with the phone because it\'s still in beta but has multitouch) is really good.'),(24,1,208,'Rather than extolling the virtues of the hardware I will comment, having been an owner of an N85 in the past, that Nokia\'s Symbian ^3 contains incremental improvements in UI and ease of use while still remaining to the delight of its fan base a very familiar OS to use.'),(25,13,401,'The screen isn\'t like my 920 but it is good enough,  FF Camera, the size is great for my purposes (an mp3 player) and it\'s great as a second device when my 920 battery runs out  which is rarely ever.I highly recommend this phone!'),(26,16,48,'I am totally disappointed with this device and I will return this crappy defensive cell phone at the UPS store tomorrow morning for a refund.'),(27,23,92,'\"Internet radio\").Nokia more or less abandoned Symbian/Nokia Belle in February 2011.'),(28,5,321,'The only items that I was not able to get out of iTunes where my tv episodes and movies.'),(29,4,227,'N8 fits your pocket very easily, the lens is quite well protected and you can buy extra cover if needed.'),(30,6,84,'The camera is so powerful and high quality; it\'s even better than Satio!!'),(31,23,99,'I have had it & will never buy another Nokia product ever again.'),(32,7,259,'I will tell you what it means for me most.The phone has excellent connectivity.'),(33,0,432,'I bought this phone for use in Jamaica, it suppose to be international version and factory unlocked.'),(34,34,72,'A huge improvement from previous version that came with Anna.'),(35,16,135,'Check out nokias website, they admit they produced faulty nokia n8\'s and they SAY that everythings okay now, but you\'ve been warned.'),(36,16,69,'For example, say you haven\'t checked your second,(or 3rd or,4th, or 5th, or 6th)home screen in a while (about 15 min to an hour).'),(37,9,201,'If you live in North America, you probably get Latin Fonts without support for CJK (Chinese, Japanese, Korean), Arabic, Hindi, Hebrew.... etc.'),(38,8,451,'Also, the back of the phone has the lens raised up a bit so it makes it a bit awkward to hold at certain angles.'),(39,19,463,'I highly recommend to anyone interested in windows platform.'),(40,1,181,'Hoping that I simply had acquired a faulty unit, I promptly exchanged the phone for a new one from Amazon.Unfortunately, the same problem persists in the second handset as well; the charging indicator light won\'t even respond.'),(41,16,175,'I feel Amazon should no longer support My-Wish-List as their products are nothing more than a bunch of knock-offs made or refurbished in China!!!'),(42,28,339,'I used the 920 when I was in Chicago and it got me where I wanted to go via buses (I know, I\'m cheap) every day with no issues (bus times, stop locations, etc).'),(43,19,345,'After having been out for two years, I expected a lot more from it.'),(44,34,76,'One could set up one touch dial to call a frequently called number or even do speech command.Emails on this phone is great.'),(45,5,245,'I streamed music through a car stereo recently, and could swear it was connected via cable, with no disruption whatsoever !!'),(46,6,134,'I could be wrong but enhancements and upgrades for that phone seemed unlikely.'),(47,19,340,'Lumia 925/928/1020 all uses the same processor.Wireless charging:I haven\'t had the chance to play with this so you\'ll have to read other people\'s review for that one.NFC:I was looking forward to this since most Android phones can share photos via NFC.'),(48,0,22,'I really like the phone, looks great, sound is great, quick learning curve, but the battery life sucks.'),(49,29,109,'[March 13th 2012]I have been using Nokia\'s Belle update for several weeks now.'),(50,1,391,'Even though the display isn\'t HD it still looks great.'),(51,24,120,'The phone itself is a work of art but slippery so I ordered a case for it.'),(52,10,134,'The size (particularly the width) and weight are perfect for using one hand to perform functions.'),(53,2,354,'I wanted to mention that the Cyan Lumia 920 I ordered from this page came glossy, not matte.'),(54,4,67,'Some applications come with the phone, some you have to download and from these, some are free, and some are not.Other features I use from the phone are wi-fi and 3G for internet connectivity, both work seamlessly.I\'ve had a lot of fun with the N8 since I got it on early November of 2010 (that\'s about 3 months ago).My previous smartphone had a slide-out keyboard and that\'s just about the only thing I miss (and just a little bit) from my old phone.The operating system on this phone is Symbian^3, which came out in 2010, so the applications developed for Symbian^3 may not yet be many, but so far this hasn\'t been an issue for me at all.I also got the Nokia CC-1005 silicone cover for my phone, i